---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Jan Ivkovic";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Jan Ivkovic</h1>
    <small>Full-Stack Engineer</small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I am a Full-Stack Engineer interested in various aspects of development and have experience in building servers, web apps, 
        mobile apps, games...
    </p>
    <p>
        The most current projects I have worked on were building a 2D online mobile game with Cloud Base Games Ltd., and in my 
        spare time I am currently building my own chat application using Swift for iOS devices, as I thing the existing solutions
        do not provide enough security and privacy so I decided to build my own simple to use end-to-end encrypted chatting 
        solution.
    </p>
    <p>
        Aside from projects, I am also conducting research utilizing WebRTC to create a more cost efficient live video streaming 
        solution that could reduce the load on servers and create more efficient live streaming platforms.
    </p>
    <div class="button">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button>My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/csharp/csharp-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="DotNetCore" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/dotnetcore/dotnetcore-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="TypeScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Angular" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/angularjs/angularjs-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Bootstrap" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/bootstrap/bootstrap-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-plain.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Ut at interdum dui. Donec ut ante ex. Maecenas id ex eget nibh consequat accumsan.
        Proin semper semper dui nec feugiat. Donec cursus neque id aliquet finibus. Morbi
        facilisis turpis nibh, nec dictum orci dictum nec. In hac habitasse platea dictumst.
        Maecenas mollis turpis vitae turpis bibendum, vitae tristique arcu eleifend.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #fdebf3;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
